QA Report – Sephora CSV Validation
-------------------------------------

* A total of 696 rows were identified in the CSV file.

* Duplicate validation was performed, and no duplicate unique IDs were found. All PDP URLs were also found to be unique.

* The dataset contains 512 unique product names.

* During the QA validation process, the following observations were made:

* For Unique ID 278072 (Balancing Treatment Lotion Toner), a total of 7 images are available on the website, whereas only 6 image URLs are present in the file.
* For Unique ID 282994, a total of 8 images are available on the website, whereas only 6 image URLs are present in the file.

